\f1\b0\fs44 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}8 ounces (2 sticks) {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/butter/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 unsalted butter}}, at room temperature\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 ounces {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/blue-cheese/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 blue cheese}}, crumbled (recommended: Maytag or Point Reyes)\
{\listtext	\'95	}4 slices smoked bacon, cooked until {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/crisp/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 crisp}} and finely chopped\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 teaspoons chopped fresh chives\
